rc=\"hanziyan-L31151.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L31152.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L31153.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L31154.png\"></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>裴</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>裴<br>péi<br>姓。<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>裴</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［péi］<br>［《廣韻》薄回切，平灰，並。］<br>亦作“裵1”。<br>(1)衣长貌。<br>(2)见“裴回”。<br>(3)姓。三国魏有裴潜。见《三国志·魏志》本传。<br>[②]［féi］<br>［《廣韻》符非切，平微，奉。］<br>古地名用字。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>裴</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【申集下】【衣字部】　裴； 康熙笔画：14； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/1119.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页1119第01</span></a><br>【唐韻】薄回切【集韻】蒲枚切，?音陪。【玉篇】長衣貌。　又姓。【通志·氏族略】裴氏，嬴姓，伯益之後，秦非子之孫，封?鄕，因以爲氏。六代孫陵，當周僖王之時，封爲解邑君，乃去邑從衣。又西域有裴氏。　又裴回，與徘徊通。【前漢·燕刺王傳】裴回兩渠閒兮，君子獨安居。　又【廣韻】符非切，音肥。卽裴，縣名。【前漢·地理志】魏郡卽裴。　又【韻會】匪微切。義同。【漢書·應劭註】音非。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>裴</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>裴</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>：1、指姓氏；2、长衣下垂的样子。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">Pei<br>Basic explanation of words<br>Pei<br>péi<br>name.<br>Pei<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［péi］<br>[\"Guangyun\" thin back cut, flat gray, combined. ]<br>Also known as \"Bao 1\".<br>(1) Dress length and appearance.<br>(2) See \"Pei Hui\".<br>(3) Last name. Three Kingdoms Wei has Pei Qian. See the biography of \"Three Kingdoms·Weizhi\".<br>[②]［féi］<br>[\"Guangyun\" Fu Feiqie, Pingwei, Feng. ]<br>Ancient place names use words.<br>Pei<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Shen Jixia] [Department of Clothing Characters] 　 Pei; Kangxi Strokes: 14; Page Number: Page 1119 No. 01<br>[Tang Yun] Thin back cut [Ji Yun] Pu Mei cut, with sound. 【Jade articles】Long clothes appearance.　Another last name. [Tongzhi·Clan Profile] Pei's surname, Ying, after Boyi, the grandson of Qin Fei's son, was named \"Yun\" because of his family name. The six generations of Sun Ling, when the king of Zhou Xi, was named Jieyi Monarch, but he went to Yi Congyi. And there is Pei in the Western Regions.　 Pei back again, communicating with Wandering. [Previous Han · Yan Chong Wang Biography] Pei Hui two channels are idle, the gentleman lives alone.　[Guangyun] Fu Feiqie, sound fat. Pei, the county name. [Pre-Han Geography] Wei Junxuan Pei.　[Yunhui] The bandit cuts slightly. The same meaning. [Han Shu·Ying Shao Note] Yin Fei.<br>Pei<br>Source glyph<br>Pei<br>Name meaning<br>:1. Refers to the surname; 2. The appearance of drooping long clothes.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274097839778.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148274097839778.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148274097839778.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">裴<br>形声字。衣表意,篆书形体像一件衣服,表示长衣下垂的样子;非(fai)表声,兼表衣不是一般的长而是很长。本义是长<br>衣下垂貌。现只作姓氏用字。<br>姓。<br>péi<br>寒裴装<br>楷<br>關</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">Пей<br>Пиктофонетические символы.<br>Одежда выражает значение. Надпись на печати подобна предмету одежды, что означает, что длинное платье опускается, выражение фаи выражает, а платье обычно не длинное, но очень длинное.<br>Первоначальный смысл - появление свисающей длинной одежды.<br>Теперь он используется только как фамилия.<br>название.<br>Наряд Хан Пей<br>Кай<br>выключать</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">péi</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><strong>I</strong> <i>собств.</i></div>\n  <div>Пэй (<i>фамилия</i>)</div>\n  <div><strong>II</strong> <i>прил. /наречие</i></div>\n  <div>полосатый; длиннополый (<i>об одежде</i>)</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">裴如 <i>уст.</i> полосатый; как полосатое платье</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"h